OL,3,CNurses who contracted long Covid still
OL,4,Cwaiting for financial support
OL,6,FThe Royal College of Nurses described
OL,7,Fthe situation as a "betrayal", as ITV
OL,8,FNews' Louisa Britton reports
OL,10,FThousands of nurses and doctors who
OL,11,Fcontracted long Covid during the
OL,12,Fpandemic are still waiting for access
OL,13,Fto financial support, according to the
OL,14,FRoyal College of Nurses (RCN).
