OL,3,CNurses who contracted long Covid still
OL,4,Cwaiting for financial support
OL,6,FThis is despite the Industrial
OL,7,FInjuries and Advisory Council (IIAC)
OL,8,Frecommending long Covid to be listed
OL,9,Fas an occupational disease two years
OL,10,Fago, which would allow those who
OL,11,Fcontracted the virus at work to apply
OL,12,Ffor extra benefits.
OL,14,FMany healthcare workers have stopped
OL,15,Fworking and taken an early retirement
OL,16,Fbecause of long Covid symptoms,
OL,17,Fleading to a huge loss in earnings.
OL,19,FThe nursing union has called this a
OL,20,F"betrayal" and is urging the
OL,21,Fgovernment to take action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
