OL,3,CNurses who contracted long Covid still
OL,4,Cwaiting for financial support
OL,6,FShe said as a result she was forced
OL,7,Finto early retirement.
OL,9,F"I can't do the job that I love doing,
OL,10,Fthat I've done for the last 25 years.
OL,11,FIt's really, really sad, but it's one
OL,12,Fof those things.
OL,14,F"And I need to move on and hopefully
OL,15,Fget a little bit better, so that I can
OL,16,Fthen get back to nursing children,
OL,17,Fwhich is what I love," she told ITV
OL,18,FNews.
