OL,3,CNurses who contracted long Covid still
OL,4,Cwaiting for financial support
OL,6,FIn 2022, the IIAC recommended Covid
OL,7,Fcomplications be recognised as an
OL,8,Foccupational disease.
OL,10,FThis would mean staff would have more
OL,11,Froutes to access Industrial Injuries
OL,12,Fand Disablement Benefits (IIDB).
OL,14,FHowever, despite IIDB covering more
OL,15,Fthan 70 diseases, Covid is still not
OL,16,Flisted, making it harder for affected
OL,17,Fstaff to access financial support.
OL,19,FLisa says she feels "completely
OL,20,Fbetrayed" by the government because
OL,21,Fthe disease still isn't listed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
