OL,3,CNurses who contracted long Covid still
OL,4,Cwaiting for financial support
OL,6,F"I am now on hardly any money. I feel
OL,7,Fthat it's something that I can try and
OL,8,Fclaim, but it's been very, very
OL,9,Fdifficult. There's been lots of
OL,10,Fhurdles.
OL,12,F"It's like everyone clapped for us.
OL,13,FBut where are they now? What are the
OL,14,Fgovernment doing now?
OL,16,F"It's really hard. And it's really
OL,17,Fhard on my family. It's like my 14-
OL,18,Fyear-old has had to become my carer.
OL,19,FShe has to do a lot of stuff for me."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
