OL,3,CNurses who contracted long Covid still
OL,4,Cwaiting for financial support
OL,6,FThe RCN has written a letter to Work
OL,7,Fand Pensions Secretary Liz Kendall
OL,8,Furging the government to act.
OL,10,FNicola Ranger, RCN General Secretary
OL,11,Fand Chief Executive Professor, told
OL,12,FITV News: "Thousands of nurses have
OL,13,Fcontacted us for support because they
OL,14,Fhave contracted long Covid and sadly
OL,15,Fmany of them have had to retire early.
OL,17,F"The careers that they love ended and
OL,18,Fsome of them are living on as much as
OL,19,F#500 a month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
