OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FWork and Pensions said: "We're
OL,8,Fcurrently carrying out a detailed
OL,9,Fassessment of the report's
OL,10,Frecommendations, and will provide a
OL,11,Fformal response once this work is
OL,12,Fcomplete.
OL,14,F"DWP offers financial support through
OL,15,FUniversal Credit and New Style
OL,16,FEmployment and Support Allowance for
OL,17,Fpeople with a health condition that
OL,18,Flimits their ability to work."
